div.div:
This text field will be a search bar. The user
will search for the stitch they need, select it
from a list, and then the resulting stitch will be
kept below it in a recently used 'palette'.
The user will select the stitch they need from the
palette and tap the place in the grid where it belongs
in the pattern. UI design still in progress.
